{"tid":1447110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人學文學] 以眼還眼","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:56:59.000Z","uid":113368,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1879ec3b77effba841f1d65e6d3b55252ceb29c1","tid":1447110,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼是希伯來《聖經》中常提到的術語，為防範犯罪、作惡、或惡意傷人者，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">意為當你令別人有甚麼損失，你也應有相應的損失</span></span></span>。「以眼還眼，以牙還牙」為傳統的同態復仇理念。 「以牙還牙，以眼還眼」也成為博弈論的一種策略，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這種策略簡單且能非常有效，被認為是解決囚徒困境的最佳策略。</span></span>&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n每日一篇文學， 中國文學果然博大精深<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: wikipedia"},{"pid":"64dc625c6ee00fa3b402d78ed971024b308589bd","tid":1447110,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"有冇人有研究中國文學？？？"},{"pid":"c77aaf04b4c8adc7c2031e044f3893c83b34bd18","tid":1447110,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人有研究中國文學？？？"},{"pid":"8a14557b934ecf2673574e552ee5fa5a5ee20f30","tid":1447110,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"以春袋還眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕佢子孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02701246b33e7858f97c97b5d607c2e24279c6a5","tid":1447110,"uid":113368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"有冇文學愛好者可以share多d文學作品俾我？"},{"pid":"aa104bd56d1921adf804622ae13a20bc135dc83c","tid":1447110,"uid":46282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"fon